cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI. 

The paper focuses on video captioning, which involves both computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) and cs.CL (Computation and Language) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also proposes a novel recurrent encoding module and a novel visual spatial feature, which involve machine learning and deep learning techniques, making cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) likely sub-categories as well. Finally, the paper aims to improve the performance of video captioning, which can be considered an application of artificial intelligence, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) a possible sub-category.
